msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:32
msgid ""
"Vagrant is not a bad way for a sysadmin to get a quick sense of how an "
"application like Dataverse is put together in a sandbox (a virtual "
"machine running on a laptop for example), but to allow end users to start"
" playing with Dataverse, you'll need to install Dataverse on a server."
