#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:66
msgid ""
"Dataverse is a Java Enterprise Edition (EE) web application that is "
"shipped as a war (web archive) file."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:69
msgid "Required Components"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:71
msgid ""
"When planning your installation you should be aware of the following "
"components of the Dataverse architecture:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:73
msgid ""
"Linux: RHEL/CentOS is highly recommended since all development and QA "
"happens on this distribution."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:74
msgid ""
"Glassfish: a Java EE application server to which the Dataverse "
"application (war file) is to be deployed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:75
msgid "PostgreSQL: a relational database."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:76
msgid "Solr: a search engine. A Dataverse-specific schema is provided."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:77
msgid "SMTP server: for sending mail for password resets and other notifications."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:78
msgid ""
"Persistent identifier service: DOI and Handle support are provided. "
"Production use requires a registered DOI or Handle.net authority."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:81
msgid "Optional Components"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:83
msgid ""
"There are a number of optional components you may choose to install or "
"configure, including:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:85
msgid ""
"R, rApache, Zelig, and TwoRavens: :doc:`/user/data-exploration/tworavens`"
" describes the feature and :doc:`r-rapache-tworavens` describes how to "
"install these components. :doc:`external-tools` explains how third-party "
"tools like TwoRavens can be added to Dataverse."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:86
msgid ""
"Dropbox integration :ref:`dataverse.dropbox.key`: for uploading files "
"from the Dropbox API."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:87
msgid ""
"Apache: a web server that can \"reverse proxy\" Glassfish applications "
"and rewrite HTTP traffic."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:88
msgid ""
"Shibboleth: an authentication system described in :doc:`shibboleth`. Its "
"use with Dataverse requires Apache."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:89
msgid "OAuth2: an authentication system described in :doc:`oauth2`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/installation/prep.rst:90
msgid ""
"Geoconnect: a system that allows users to create maps from geospatial "
"files, described in :doc:`geoconnect`."
